[{"Id": 1014877, "EnglishTitle": null, "GujaratiTitle": null, "RUrduTitle": null, "UrduTitle": null, "Sequence": 1, "EnglishDescription": "Imam Kazim (a) is also reported to have said, “Whoever places (the recitation of) <Surah Ikhlaas> between him and any tyrannical person, Almighty Allah will save him from that person. Whoever recites <Surah Ikhlaas> in front of him (self), to his backside, to his right side, and to his left side, Almighty Allah will provide him with his good things and will prevent his evil things to reach him.”", "GujaratiDescription": null, "RUrduDescription": "Imam Kazim (a) ne farmaaya keh jo shakhs <Surah Ikhlaas> ko apne aur zaalim shakhs ke darmiyaan padhega to Haq taala usey uske shar se mehfooz rakhega. Is Surah ko apne aage, peechhe, daaye’n, baaye’n padhe aur phir us zaalim o jaabir ke saamne jaaye to Allah taala usey us ki taraf se achchhayi dikhaayega aur uski buraayi se bachaayega.", "UrduDescription": "امام موسیٰ کاظم ؑ نے فرمایا : جو شخص <سورۂ اخلاص> کو اپنے اور ظالم شخص کے درمیان پڑھے گا تو حق تعالیٰ اسے اس کے شر سے محفوظ رکھے گااس سورہ کو اپنے آگے پیچھے اور دائیں بائیں پڑھے اور پھر اس ظالم و جابر کے سامنے جائے تو اﷲتعالیٰ اسے اس کی طرف سے اچھائی دکھائے گااور اس کی برائی سے بچائے گا۔", "English": null, "Gujarati": null, "RGujarati": null, "RUrdu": null, "Urdu": null, "RArabic": null, "ArabicText1": null, "ArabicGreenSign1": null, "ArabicRedSign1": null, "ArabicBlueSign1": null, "ArabicText2": null, "ArabicGreenSign2": null, "ArabicRedSign2": null, "ArabicBlueSign2": null, "ArabicText3": null, "ArabicGreenSign3": null, "ArabicRedSign3": null, "ArabicBlueSign3": null, "ArabicText4": null, "ArabicGreenSign4": null, "ArabicRedSign4": null, "ArabicBlueSign4": null, "ArabicText5": null, "ArabicGreenSign5": null, "ArabicRedSign5": null, "ArabicBlueSign5": null, "ArabicText6": null, "ArabicGreenSign6": null, "ArabicRedSign6": null, "ArabicBlueSign6": null, "ArabicText7": null, "ArabicGreenSign7": null, "ArabicRedSign7": null, "ArabicBlu